'''Vira606''' was a synthetic virus manufactured for the [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|Imperial Security Bureau]]. It was always fatal, and although it was not contagious, there was no cure. It could be kept in remittance through regular injections of a serum developed to counteract its effects, however.<ref name="Orbit">{{WEGCite|story=Preparing for War|book=The Far Orbit Project}}</ref>

[[Vocis Kenit]] infected the [[Solar Terrors]] with Vira606 and rationed out the serum as the pirates performed requested tasks.<ref name="Orbit" />

